<div class="section-title">Dub Mixer Simulation</div>
<div class="section-sub">The dub engineer treats the mixing desk as an instrument. Faders arc through the mix, sends feed echo chambers and reverbs, and every voltage is a creative decision. Drop — the instrument disappears. Cut — the echo eats itself.</div>
